OL,6,FJudge Mr Justice Choudhury thanked the
OL,7,Fjury for their service and said
OL,8,FCarless would be sentenced on Thursday.
OL,10,FNarmina Rafiq of the Crown Prosecution
OL,11,FService said: "This was a truly awful
OL,12,Fcase that shows just how severe and
OL,13,Fcalculated domestic violence can be.
OL,14,FKirsty Carless did not have a sudden
OL,15,Foutburst, instead this was a
OL,16,Fdeliberate and premeditated killing,
OL,17,Ffollowing a series of events that
OL,18,Fbegan with jealousy over Louis Price's
OL,19,Fuse of dating apps and ended in murder.
