OL,6,F"The Crown Prosecution Service built a
OL,7,Fcompelling case using DNA evidence,
OL,8,FCCTV footage, witness testimony,
OL,9,Fforensic tests and pathological
OL,10,Fevidence that not only proved Kirsty
OL,11,FCarless intended to kill Mr Price but
OL,12,Fshowed exactly how it happened,
OL,13,Fleaving the jury certain of her guilt.
OL,15,F"Her unbelievably cruel and heartless
OL,16,Factions have robbed six children of
OL,17,Ftheir father and his parents of their
OL,18,Fbeloved son. We hope today's outcome
OL,19,Fbrings them some comfort. Our
OL,20,Fcondolences remain with Mr Price's
